data.description: Impeccable, enchanting, historical and authentic Victorian, thoughtfully and meticulously restored and updated. Grand foyer entry with custom-carved staircase. Double ribbons of walnut inlaid in oak floors. Beveled stained glass windows in stairway, front parlor, and den. New kitchen with quartz counters, 6 burner gas range, farmhouse sink and stainless-steel appliances. Updated main full bath with double sink. Upper-level features 4 bedrooms and ¾ bath with subway tile and quartz vanity. Oversized primary bedroom with working fireplace, office/nursery, walk-in closet. 3rd floor offers huge finished bonus room. Private back yard with patio, 1 ½ car garage. Newer AC, furnace and roof.
